        "created_at": "2023-01-03T20:55:29.746Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hello FoundationDB community,</p>\n<p>I would like to ask if it\u2019s possible to start with just one server <em>(being aware of the risks)</em>, working with it <em>(saving and working with data)</em> and, later, add another server (or two, three), changing the cluster configuration and operation mode.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 3,
        "updated_at": "2023-01-03T20:55:29.746Z",
